data.description: Welcome to Carriage Oaks S/D! What a Stunning Acadian Style Home with a New Orleans Twist. Home features approximately 2100 sq. ft. htd. And approximately 3000 sq. ft. under roof. This 4-bedroom 2.5 bath home has all the bells and whistles that you come to enjoy. Granite countertops, wood/ceramic flooring, cozy fireplace, and relaxing back patio with a great view of a HUGE back yard.   There is Custom Woodwork throughout. Bonus room with half bath is located above garage. Schedule your showing today!!
